data.description: WOW This home has everything! 5 bedrooms, 2 living rooms, 3.5 bathrooms & POOL! Immaculately maintained w/ new flooring, carpet & interior/exterior paint. Main living room is finished w/ wood-tile floors & a vaulted ceiling. Kitchen is huge, w/ tons of storage & counterspace ~ breakfast bar, double ovens, refrigerator, large eating space. Just off the kitchen is a great flexible space ~ 2nd living area or dining area & features a beautiful fireplace. Master suite is very spacious ~ overlooks the pool ~ 2 closets, double vanities, separate shower & bathtub. 2nd bedroom on the 1st level ~ walk-in closet ~ would also make a great study. 2nd floor has an additional huge living room & 3 bedrooms ~ all with large closets as well. The tranquil backyard features a 40,000 gal pool & a private patio to relax. The 3 car garage is fully insulated ~ upgraded storm shelter, workshop & attic space is fully decked. Extra insulation added to home for amazing energy efficiency! Welcome Home!
